{"tid":360996,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"任職數據中心 陳白山：坐監累全港網絡","createTime":"2017-08-15T17:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T00:18:26.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0bc76630bfb9e1cf540ed0e92c141ca3d425b182","tid":360996,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:50:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20151231/s00002/1451499516753\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20151231%2Fs00002%2F1451499516753&d=kTTBxhKuG1eO8%2BXVsyK9QgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=cfadfb4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20151231%2Fs00002%2F1451499516753&h=7d50caa2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20151231/s00002/1451499516753</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】12名被告當中，除陳白山外，其餘被告均聘請律師代表。陳白山自行求情時稱，自己在17間數據中心任職以支援工作為主的維修員，若他被判處入獄，全港網絡將受影響，後果將會很嚴重。裁判官溫紹明回應﹕「你嚇我呀？我都唔知咩係數據中心，你嚇唔到我。」溫官又查間陳是否不想坐監，陳回應﹕「以監禁形式唔係咁好。」<br />\n<br />\n陳白山說，案發時他只是手持雨傘，卻被噴胡椒噴霧，反問溫官：「我有咩暴力行為？」又指他若被重判，有關判刑則是在恐嚇其他示威者及有訴求的人。溫官語帶無奈地說﹕「唉！你唔好諗到自己咁重要。」陳其後說，自己在事件中只是小角色，參與少，但強調不認為法庭在任何情况下，可以做到政治中立。溫官一再強調，法庭不是處理政治的地方，惟陳反駁﹕「但係你𠵱家就係處理緊政治。」溫官最終慨嘆﹕「我幾希望你有律師代表，咁我就唔使同你直接對話。」<br />\n<br />\n官：嚇唔到我 唔好諗到自己咁重要<br />\n<br />\n溫官昨允許另外兩名被告黃浩銘及何潔泓親自求情。黃於陳辭時說，外界認為即使他們多麼不滿意政府，也不應該干犯本案，他理解外界的想法。溫官隨即說﹕「我好多嘢唔講得。」又指法庭在處理案件時保持中立，當法官於庭內討論政治時，則法庭已不再中立。"},{"pid":"43267f4efa50311c054ee2154ee7c62c65465e91","tid":360996,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144ba1dcb139746e57b4ccffbd20e79c5482c0aa","tid":360996,"uid":29014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T18:06:32.000Z","msg":"點解近排d法官講野越講越on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c834f4f4b972ff0ba9d6b8fde82f9d08a2e12d","tid":360996,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T18:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解近排d法官講野越講越on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2年前架戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee2859c87d9134d89f751e7f5511df72e7fee60","tid":360996,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:10:04.000Z","msg":"兩邊都<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11813478ab209bb19f57ec6f47fb1f98568abc44","tid":360996,"uid":82291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:15:51.000Z","msg":"個法官連數據中心都唔知係乜？<br />\n佢地係咪只要求有法律知識就足夠做法官，其他乜都唔洗知架？"},{"pid":"1ea73a5f09be08232970461d909e9d7471dccaa7","tid":360996,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:18:07.000Z","msg":"邊個教佢講咁on9理由"},{"pid":"bf1dc3527d28845db72aec0ea5ed8cfb90d24de8","tid":360996,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T00:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解近排d法官講野越講越on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2年前架戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9都唔係第一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}